Goooooood question!

Anyway, this is my latest skip after taking a long time off to not write skips. It's super long, so if that isn't your kind of thing it's cool! If not, then I hope you enjoy it!

Thanks to everybody in chat who checked it out and gave advice. I really appreciate it!

